OL,4,CEx-Nissan boss Carlos Ghosn: How I
OL,5,Cescaped Japan in a box
OL,6, At 10.30pm on a cold December night in
OL,7, 2019, a former titan of the global car
OL,8, industry lay bundled inside a box on
OL,9, board a plane, waiting to flee Japan.
OL,11,F"The plane was scheduled to take off at
OL,12,F11pm," recalls Carlos Ghosn.
OL,14,F"The 30 minutes waiting in the box on
OL,15,Fthe plane, waiting for it to take off,
OL,16,Fwas probably the longest wait I've ever
OL,17,Fexperienced in my life."
OL,19,FNow, for the first time, the man who
OL,20,Fwas once the boss of both Nissan and
OL,21,FRenault has detailed his daring escape.
